## 3. Building a Knowledge Graph with an LLM

### Pipeline
```
Unstructured Text
      │
      ▼
[Named Entity Recognition (NER)] ──► Entities (nodes)
      │
      ▼
[Relation Extraction] ──► Relationships (edges)
      │
      ▼
[Entity Linking / Coreference Resolution] ──► Canonical entities
      │
      ▼
[Knowledge Cleaning] ──► Remove duplicates, resolve conflicts
      │
      ▼
[Knowledge Enrichment] ──► Add properties, link to external KGs
      │
      ▼
[Neo4j / Graph DB] ──► Hosted knowledge graph
```

### LLM-Assisted KG Construction
- Prompt LLM to extract entity-relation triples from raw text
- Use structured output (JSON schema) for consistent triple format
- Validate against ontology schema before ingesting
- **Knowledge assessment**: Evaluate completeness and accuracy
- **Knowledge cleaning**: Deduplicate entities, normalise names
- **Knowledge hosting**: Deploy in Neo4j; expose via API

